::Dark One::

Dark One's internal scanners report Squizzy's actions, the Oblitercon 
frowning. With a silent command, all the consoles in the cockpit are 
deactivated, Dark One flying on.

"I'm afraid I can't let you edject," he says as panels cover the console, the 
lever pulling itself down and a panel covering it as well. Dark One flies on, 
a bit annoyed at the bot's actions.
